name: Master Class: Expedited Analysis
description:
For those already familiar with UserTesting, this course will help you continue to hone your capabilities for analyzing and summarizing the results of your tests.

This course includes:


  • Tips for effective analysis
  • Pro-tips for using features in the platform (including metrics, transcripts, and the Export to Excel feature)
  • Guidance on sharing findings
  • Practical examples of findings and insights
